params.name: threshold
params.description: Score threshold to keep object detection predictions.

params.name: target_sizes
params.description: Tensor of shape (batch_size, 2) or list of tuples (Tuple[int, int]) containing the target size(height, width) of each image in the batch. If left to None, predictions will not be resized.

params.name: top_k
params.description: Keep only top k bounding boxes before filtering by thresholding.
